criticized the Israeli government's decision to arm the settlers
and said the shooting showed the real murderousness of the
settlers.
</P>
<P>
VOP quoted Karabesh's mother as saying that the settler
began shooting at the students at random.
</P>
<P>
Israeli police said they are investigating the incident and
could not give the reason behind the shooting.
</P>
<P>
Katabesh was buried Thursday afternoon by his family while
the condition of the injured Jabareen was stable after being
treated at hospital.
</P>
<P>
Mutual distrust and hatred have been mounting between the
Palestinians and Israelis as no breakthrough in the Mideast peace
process has been achieved for a long period.
</P>
<P>
On August 20, Jewish settler Rabbi Shlomo Ra'anan was stabbed
to death at his home in Hebron.
</P>
<P>
On August 4, two Jewish settlers of Yithar settlement near
Nablus, the West Bank, were shot to death. 
