<HEADLINE> Ugandans Urged to Learn Computer Skills </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KAMPALA, September 17 (Xinhua) -- Ugandans have been urged to
learn computer skills as a means of accessing and processing
information.
</P>
<P>
