<P>
Jiang expressed the hope that bilateral cooperation will
continue to be developed and the CISCO will score even greater
successes.
</P>
<P>
The CISCO is one of the world's leading internetwork equipment
manufacturers. Chambers is expected to discuss cooperation matters
with the Ministry of Education during his current China tour.
</P>
<P>
