relief measures in Japan's 1998 fiscal year, the Japanese Embassy
here said Friday.
</P>
<P>
The basic objective of the debt relief grant is to assist the
Nepali government in procuring essential commodities like
petroleum products, fertilizer, medicine, communication survey and
construction equipment and transportation equipment that are
required in the development activities of Nepal, the embassy said
in a press release.
