Fox's current contract with the ISU to telecast the Grand Prix
events runs out after this season. Figure skating has been a
popular event in the United States. The world figure skating
championships and the Goodwill Games figure skating competition
have attracted many Americans viewers this year. America Michelle
Kwan is the current wolrd women's figure skating champion.
