economic loss from German Foreign Minister Klaus Kinkel's
instigation in the European Union to impose sanctions on the
Yugoslav federation.
</P>
<P>
Kinkel's stance has helped boost the morale of the Kosovo
separatists and terrorists, the note said.
</P>
<P>
Such statements by the German foreign and defense ministers are
not helpful to the stability of Europe and the Balkan region in
particular, the note said. 
